Review_Text: Used Samsung Galaxy S24 5G extensively for over 20 days. In compariosn of iPhone 16, the S24 stand nowhere near to iPhone 16 in terms UI, security, Camera etc.The landing screen of both the phone is highly different and iPhone stands class apart. In terms of frequent notification, iPhone display it in a very nice way without actually opening the phone which is completely lacking in S24. The onlu feature of S24 is use of dual camera while recording is something not available in iPhone. Further...READ MORE

Overall it's fine, camera, sound quality,performance is good.....charging is too slow. Takes almost 2 mins for charging 1% with 35W charger, but notification says fast charging. Disappointed with battery performance too.READ MORE
